data.description: Welcome to 717 Los Miradores, located in a private gated community in the Colinas Coronado Subdivision! Situated on an impressive 13,226 sq/ft trophy lot, this property offers captivating views of the Franklin Mountains and stunning sunset views of the Upper Valley. The home features a timeless design for open entertainment and everyday activities, flooded with natural light and views from nearly every window. With 4 spacious bedrooms and an office with versatile uses, the layout is both functional and flexible. The gourmet kitchen boasts built-in appliances, granite countertops, and a large island with a generous overhang for dining. Movie nights are enhanced by the built-in speaker system, and the 8-foot sliding doors create a seamless indoor-outdoor experience. Absolutely gorgeous backyard featuring a spacious covered patio and a refreshing heated pool that provides year-round enjoyment. Additionally, a bonus exterior gas line has been added for outdoor barbecuing.
